 from CDN only when needed"},"310":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-40","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Automatic caching**: Once loaded, icons are cached for optimal performance"},"311":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-41","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Flexible sizing**: Support for `width` and `height` props"},"312":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-42","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Color inheritance**: Uses `currentColor` by default for seamless theme integration"},"313":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-43","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Accessibility ready**: Built-in support for screen readers and keyboard navigation"},"314":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-44","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"},"315":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-45","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Bento integration**: Extends Bento Icon with additional Antares-specific features"},"316":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-46","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#props","content":"The `Icon` component accepts the following props:"},"317":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-47","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"The component extends `BentoIconProps` and passes through all standard HTML attributes and accessibility props to the underlying Bento Icon component. This includes:"},"318":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-48","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Accessibility**: `aria-label`, `aria-describedby`, `role`, `title`"},"319":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-49","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Events**: `onClick`, `onMouseOver`, `onFocus`, etc."},"320":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-50","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"},"321":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-51","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Transform**: `rotate`, `flip` for icon transformations"},"322":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-52","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#size-variants","content":"Specify explicit width and height values:"},"323":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-53","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#size-variants","content":"You can use different values for width and height:"},"324":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-54","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#slots","content":"The Icon component uses Bento's slot system with the following component hierarchy and available slot override points:"},"325":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-55","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"**`icon`**: Overrides the entire BentoIcon component - affects icon loading, caching, sprite/SVG mode switching, data attributes, and the overall icon wrapper"},"326":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-56","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"**`icon.content`**: Overrides the BentoIllustration component - affects SVG transformations (rotate, flip), accessibility attributes (`role`, `focusable`, `aria-labelledby`), viewBox calculations, and final SVG element rendering"},"327":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-57","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"For complete slot override patterns and examples, see the `@bento/slots` package documentation."},"328":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-58","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icons","content":"While the Icon component loads design system approved icons from the CDN by default, teams can introduce custom icons using the underlying Bento Icon system."},"329":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-59","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#adding-icons-synchronously","content":"Use the `set` method to add custom icons that are available immediately:"},"330":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-60","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#adding-icons-asynchronously","content":"Use the `ondemand` method to load custom icons from your own sources:"},"331":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-61","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"The following methods are exported from `@godaddy/antares` for custom icon management:"},"332":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-62","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`set(icons)`**: Synchronously add icons to the store"},"333":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-63","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`ondemand(loader)`**: Register an asynchronous icon loader (returns unregister function)"},"334":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-64","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`parser(svgString)`**: Parse SVG strings into React elements"},"335":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-65","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"These are re-exports of the underlying Bento Icon system methods. For complete API documentation, advanced usage patterns, and implementation details, see the `@bento/icon` and `@bento/svg-parser` package documentation."},"336":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-66","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons integrate seamlessly with all Icon component features (transformations, accessibility, sprite mode, etc.)"},"337":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-67","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Multiple `ondemand` loaders can be registered and will be called in order until one returns content"},"338":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-68","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Use the `parser` function to convert SVG strings to React elements"},"339":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-69","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons are cached automatically just like CDN icons"},"340":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-70","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#css-classes","content":"The component accepts standard `className` and `style` props:"},"341":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-71","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#css-classes","content":"**Important**: When you supply a `className`, you make a commitment to take over all styling of the component as it will remove the standard class names. Use data attributes for targeted styling instead."},