reen readers:"},"360":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-90","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#semantic-icons","content":"For icons that convey meaning, use the `title` prop. This automatically adds `role=\"img\"` and provides screen reader accessible text:"},"361":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-91","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#interactive-icons","content":"For interactive icons within buttons or links, use the `title` prop on the icon and `aria-label` on the interactive element:"},"362":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-92","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"Icons are loaded on-demand from a CDN using the following process:"},"363":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-93","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**First Request**: When an icon is first encountered, it triggers an asynchronous fetch from the CDN"},"364":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-94","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"},"365":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-95","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**Automatic Caching**: Once loaded, the icon is cached in memory to avoid subsequent network requests"},"366":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-96","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**Full SVG Rendering**: Each icon instance renders as a complete SVG element with all path data"},"367":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-97","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loa